    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🔥🔥🔥THE NEW CHALLENGING CLIMBING GAME IS WAITING FOR YOU🔥🔥🔥</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Ascendrix will give you nothing but the real challenge. You need to beat the dynamic hard route of multiple-sectioned tower.  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >⚡️Explore the cyberspace locations with hard trap and obstacle mechanics⚡️</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >⚡️&quot;Watch your step!&quot; is a rule №1, and &quot;Hurry up!&quot; is a rule №2⚡️</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >⚡️Catch the right moments to move or jump⚡️</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >⚡️Fall and get more rage every time it's happened⚡️</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >And, of course,  Hardcore Mode is waiting for you, if you're tough enough or lack of pure rage 🔥</p>",
